snippet.title: Comicbook.com
snippet.description:
ComicBook.com is a division of ViacomCBS focused on all things pop culture, influenced by the robust comic book industry, whose iconic creations have become the driving force of mainstream entertainment behind today's blockbuster movies, hit TV shows, best selling video games, and more.

ComicBook.com provides fans with the latest news, reviews, tv & movie database, vibrant communities, social platforms, events and industry scoop through innovative technology products and mobile platforms.
